nodes.text: Joshua Jinzler was a patron of the Outlander Club when Jedi Anakin Skywalker and Obi-Wan Kenobi were pursuing the bounty hunter Zam Wesell. Jinzler had short, almost white hair and was wearing a reddish vest. He was part of the crowd that approached Zam's crashed Koro-2 all-environment exodrive airspeeder.
He may be a member of the same Jinzler family as Dean and Lorana Jinzler.
It is possible that this character was named after writer/editor Jonathan W. Rinzler.
